{"word":"G411 - ἀνεκδιήγητος - anekdiḗgētos - an-ek-dee-ay'-gay-tos - Unspeakable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνεκδιήγητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anekdiḗgētos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ek-dee-ay'-gay-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unspeakable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சொல்லிமுடியாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"unspeakable, indescribable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G1555 - ἐκδιηγέομαι - ekdiēgéomai - ek-dee-ayg-eh'-om-ahee/1555\">G1555</a>; <i>not expounded</i> in full, that is, <i>indescribable:</i> - unspeakable.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}